text: The ball is under the table next to the chair.
A beautiful colorful painting hangs on the wall.
The dog ran between the trees toward the house.
The soft fluffy pillow feels comfortable.
The bird flew above the clouds in the sky.
A tall dark building stands in the distance.
The car is parked behind the building.
The round red apple looks delicious.
The path goes around the lake to the right.
A bright shiny coin glimmers in the sun.
The shelf is above the desk below the window.
The thick heavy book contains many pages.
The cat sits in front of the door.
A smooth polished stone feels cold.
The bridge crosses over the river.
The small delicate flower has many petals.
The store is located near the park.
A rough textured surface provides good grip.
The road goes along the coast to the north.
The large square window lets in light.
